Live big, think big.

00:09:29.110 --> 00:09:33.020 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: What is the number
one success principle?

00:09:33.020 --> 00:09:33.960 align:middle line:90%
What would you say?

00:09:33.960 --> 00:09:35.230 align:middle line:84%
>>CANFIELD: Well, let
me ask you a question.

00:09:35.230 --> 00:09:37.240 align:middle line:84%
If you can only keep
one organ in your body,

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:39.234 align:middle line:90%
