carpet, and the bill collector's

00:32:56.540 --> 00:32:57.040 align:middle line:90%
coming.

00:32:57.040 --> 00:32:58.985 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Sucks us back
down to this dimension.

00:32:58.985 --> 00:33:01.194 align:middle line:84%
>>CANFIELD: But if you
go in there every day

00:33:01.194 --> 00:33:02.860 align:middle line:84%
with some kind of
practice, whether it's

00:33:02.860 --> 00:33:05.172 align:middle line:84%
meditation, or Tai Chi,
or walking on the ocean,

00:33:05.172 --> 00:33:07.130 align:middle line:84%
everyone has their own
way of getting in there.

00:33:07.130 --> 00:33:10.490 align:middle line:84%
Some is physical, some visual,
some auditory, chanting,

00:33:10.490 --> 00:33:11.970 align:middle line:90%
whatever.

00:33:11.970 --> 00:33:14.070 align:middle line:84%
I will share this
one little thing.

00:33:14.070 --> 00:33:16.950 align:middle line:84%
When I was in this
experience with the shaman,

00:33:16.950 --> 00:33:18.830 align:middle line:84%
I just was there,
and all of a sudden

00:33:18.830 --> 00:33:20.850 align:middle line:90%
it was this explosion of light.

00:33:20.850 --> 00:33:23.140 align:middle line:84%
And then you know how they
call it the voice of God

00:33:23.140 --> 00:33:23.806 align:middle line:90%
at a conference?

00:33:23.806 --> 00:33:27.090 align:middle line:84%
It says, "Ladies and gentlemen,
please take your seats.

00:33:27.090 --> 00:33:28.390 align:middle line:90%
Robin Williams."

00:33:28.390 --> 00:33:31.040 align:middle line:84%
So all of a sudden, I
heard this voice go,

00:33:31.040 --> 00:33:34.859 align:middle line:84%
"You are about to experience
what very few people on Earth

00:33:34.859 --> 00:33:35.775 align:middle line:90%
will ever experience."

00:33:35.775 --> 00:33:38.890 align:middle line:90%
And it went--

00:33:38.890 --> 00:33:41.700 align:middle line:90%
And I was just like, oh, my God.

00:33:41.700 --> 00:33:44.850 align:middle line:90%
And it really is, oh, my God.

00:33:44.850 --> 00:33:50.500 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Yeah, it is, because
God is that whole entire space.

00:33:50.500 --> 00:33:52.430 align:middle line:90%
And it's so vast.

00:33:52.430 --> 00:33:54.310 align:middle line:90%
It's so vast.

00:33:54.310 --> 00:33:57.630 align:middle line:84%
And interestingly
enough, I went to Asia.

00:33:57.630 --> 00:34:01.840 align:middle line:84%
I was in California in the
bottom of a mountain, fallen,

00:34:01.840 --> 00:34:04.759 align:middle line:90%
and I went to Asia in my mind.

00:34:04.759 --> 00:34:06.550 align:middle line:84%
>>CANFIELD: Sounds like
a John Denver song.

00:34:06.550 --> 00:34:08.914 align:middle line:84%
(SINGING) Went to
Asia in my mind.

00:34:08.914 --> 00:34:10.670 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Exactly!

00:34:10.670 --> 00:34:16.389 align:middle line:84%
But interestingly enough,
fast forward 15 years later.

00:34:16.389 --> 00:34:20.219 align:middle line:84%
I'm in Asia with it
dear, dear friend

00:34:20.219 --> 00:34:24.239 align:middle line:90%
who tried to die on the beach.

00:34:24.239 --> 00:34:28.530 align:middle line:84%
And I held his hand
during that moment,

00:34:28.530 --> 00:34:30.800 align:middle line:84%
and it was in Asia
that that happened,

00:34:30.800 --> 00:34:36.360 align:middle line:84%
and I watched him transition
out and in that space.

00:34:36.360 --> 00:34:37.969 align:middle line:90%
And the soul knew.

00:34:37.969 --> 00:34:41.110 align:middle line:90%
My soul knew that.

00:34:41.110 --> 00:34:42.389 align:middle line:90%
It's there.

00:34:42.389 --> 00:34:45.739 align:middle line:84%
We watched Scarlett Lewis talk
the other day about her son,

00:34:45.739 --> 00:34:50.469 align:middle line:84%
Jesse, whose life was taken
in the Sandy Hook tragedy,

00:34:50.469 --> 00:34:53.969 align:middle line:84%
