precognitive drawings

00:34:53.969 --> 00:34:58.310 align:middle line:84%
of this killer that he
had drawn before he died.

00:34:58.310 --> 00:35:00.542 align:middle line:90%
That how the soul knows.

00:35:00.542 --> 00:35:02.750 align:middle line:84%
I know this is an interview
about goal setting, Jack,

00:35:02.750 --> 00:35:05.950 align:middle line:84%
but I want to ask you
how does the soul know?

00:35:05.950 --> 00:35:07.230 align:middle line:90%
What do you think?

00:35:07.230 --> 00:35:08.280 align:middle line:90%
Your soul knows.

00:35:08.280 --> 00:35:10.050 align:middle line:84%
>>CANFIELD: Well, I'll tell
you an interesting story.

00:35:10.050 --> 00:35:11.633 align:middle line:84%
When I was in college
I had a roommate

00:35:11.633 --> 00:35:14.530 align:middle line:84%
whose father was very eccentric,
and every 10 years, he

00:35:14.530 --> 00:35:15.102 align:middle line:90%
wrote a book.

00:35:15.102 --> 00:35:16.810 align:middle line:84%
He'd study for 10
years and write a book.

00:35:16.810 --> 00:35:18.476 align:middle line:84%
He'd written a book
on the Piri Reis map

00:35:18.476 --> 00:35:21.532 align:middle line:84%
which they found predated
any exploration like Columbus

00:35:21.532 --> 00:35:22.490 align:middle line:90%
or any of those people.

00:35:22.490 --> 00:35:23.550 align:middle line:84%
He spent 10 years
trying to figure out

00:35:23.550 --> 00:35:26.270 align:middle line:84%
who was it that came over here
and drew the inland waterways

00:35:26.270 --> 00:35:28.380 align:middle line:90%
of America and all that?

00:35:28.380 --> 00:35:31.940 align:middle line:84%
When he died, he was working on
a book called "My First Million

00:35:31.940 --> 00:35:34.380 align:middle line:84%
Years," and he
was having himself

00:35:34.380 --> 00:35:35.987 align:middle line:90%
hypnotically age regressed.

00:35:35.987 --> 00:35:37.570 align:middle line:84%
He went all the way
back to coming out

00:35:37.570 --> 00:35:40.420 align:middle line:84%
of the ocean as an amphibian
with pure memory of that.

00:35:40.420 --> 00:35:42.800 align:middle line:84%
But what happened was in
hypnotic age regression,

00:35:42.800 --> 00:35:44.300 align:middle line:84%
they bring you back
by saying you're

00:35:44.300 --> 00:35:45.674 align:middle line:84%
coming forward in
time and space,

00:35:45.674 --> 00:35:47.000 align:middle line:90%
coming forward in time space.

00:35:47.000 --> 00:35:48.620 align:middle line:90%
He went into the future.

00:35:48.620 --> 00:35:51.730 align:middle line:84%
And he was at the airport, and
he read the headline on a paper

00:35:51.730 --> 00:35:53.350 align:middle line:84%
that said something
about an air crash

00:35:53.350 --> 00:35:55.790 align:middle line:84%
or whatever it was three
days into the future.

00:35:55.790 --> 00:35:57.790 align:middle line:84%
And three days
later, that happened.

00:35:57.790 --> 00:36:00.860 align:middle line:84%
Now in order for
that, you either--

00:36:00.860 --> 00:36:03.520 align:middle line:84%
what he ended up believing
after all of his research

00:36:03.520 --> 00:36:06.220 align:middle line:84%
is that all time is
happening simultaneously.

00:36:06.220 --> 00:36:09.420 align:middle line:84%
The future, the present, and
the past all exist right now.

00:36:09.420 --> 00:36:11.970 align:middle line:84%
So just the way you
can go into the past,

00:36:11.970 --> 00:36:13.750 align:middle line:90%
you can also go into the future.

00:36:13.750 --> 00:36:15.310 align:middle line:84%
It's not like it's
going out there.

00:36:15.310 --> 00:36:17.910 align:middle line:84%
It's like layers of this all
happening at the same time,

00:36:17.910 --> 00:36:21.350 align:middle line:90%
and you just tune into that.

00:36:21.350 --> 00:36:22.840 align:middle line:90%
That's my theory, anyway.

00:36:22.840 --> 00:36:24.530 align:middle line:84%
I liked the way he
explained it best.

00:36:24.530 --> 00:36:26.120 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's what
kind of goals are

00:36:26.120 --> 00:36:29.587 align:middle line:84%
is it's setting into the
future what can happen.

00:36:29.587 --> 00:36:31.295 align:middle line:84%
And if you align
yourself with meditation

00:36:31.295 --> 00:36:33.503 align:middle line:84%
and you're taught consciousness
practices that you're

00:36:33.503 --> 00:36:36.410 align:middle line:84%
talking about, you can
actually align yourself

00:36:36.410 --> 00:36:39.364 align:middle line:84%
with it actually manifesting,
with it actually happening.

00:36:39.364 --> 00:36:41.530 align:middle line:84%
>>CANFIELD: Well, something
one of the speakers here

00:36:41.530 --> 00:36:43.780 align:middle line:84%
at this conference we're
attending where we're filming

00:36:43.780 --> 00:36:48.640 align:middle line:84%
