00:36:57.670 --> 00:37:00.480 align:middle line:84%
Well, it's either a
limiting belief, or a fear,

00:37:00.480 --> 00:37:03.270 align:middle line:84%
or some anger, or
some energy that's

00:37:03.270 --> 00:37:06.990 align:middle line:84%
not of love manifestation
