00:37:06.990 --> 00:37:09.020 align:middle line:84%
And so all the
techniques, if you

00:37:09.020 --> 00:37:10.820 align:middle line:84%
don't have enough of
the openness, that's

00:37:10.820 --> 00:37:14.490 align:middle line:84%
why the work on belief's, the
work on overcoming your fears,

00:37:14.490 --> 00:37:17.920 align:middle line:84%
releasing, all the technologies
