And so many people are pushing,
pushing, pushing, pushing.

00:37:22.150 --> 00:37:25.210 align:middle line:84%
But what I find as you
open up this space,

00:37:25.210 --> 00:37:26.860 align:middle line:84%
it's almost like
your drawn forward.

