about here, the consciousness

00:43:00.600 --> 00:43:01.190 align:middle line:90%
and the goals.

00:43:01.190 --> 00:43:06.050 align:middle line:84%
That personal development
and self-development worlds

00:43:06.050 --> 00:43:08.737 align:middle line:84%
have really
combined, I believe--

00:43:08.737 --> 00:43:11.070 align:middle line:84%
