00:44:35.837 --> 00:44:38.420 align:middle line:84%
and as soon as he got that-- he
was hit in the side of the car

00:44:38.420 --> 00:44:41.644 align:middle line:84%
and couldn't walk, and yet using
visualization and affirmations,

00:44:41.644 --> 00:44:43.060 align:middle line:84%
as she learned
from this book, was

00:44:43.060 --> 00:44:45.340 align:middle line:84%
able to walk down the
