00:44:46.370 --> 00:44:49.220 align:middle line:84%
All the doctors saying that's
impossible, you can't do it.

00:44:49.220 --> 00:44:52.310 align:middle line:84%
But my favorite story,
I'm in Manila teaching

00:44:52.310 --> 00:44:54.269 align:middle line:84%
in the Philippines,
