Every single chapter, I'm going
to do everything for one year.

00:46:23.560 --> 00:46:25.268 align:middle line:84%
And if it doesn't
work, I've lost a year.

00:46:25.268 --> 00:46:27.510 align:middle line:84%
If it does work, I want to
be as successful as him.

00:46:27.510 --> 00:46:29.051 align:middle line:84%
So he did it,
every single thing.

00:46:29.051 --> 00:46:31.550 align:middle line:84%
I don't know anyone else who's
ever done every single thing.

00:46:31.550 --> 00:46:32.716 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: So it was his Bible.

